 
CONFIGURATION/ADMINISTRATION:
sudo                superuser
    EDITOR=nano visudo
        (Uncomment Wheel)
nano                editor
vim                 editor
htop                system monitor
networkmanager      network management
    NetworkManager.service
grub efibootmgr     bootloader
    grub-install --target=x86_64-efi --efi-directory=/efi --bootloader-id=grub_uefi
    grub-mkconfig -o /boot/grub/grub.cfg

DESKTOP ENVIRONMENT:
xorg-server         window manager
nvidia              video card driver
plasma              kde plasma
    sddm.service
(plasma apps)       (see kde_apps.txt)

* Use '--needed' to prevent reinstalling pkgs

UTILITIES/SECURITY:
gnupg               gpg key management
openssh             ssh client/server
firewalld           firewall 'front-end' to nftables
    firewalld.service
firejail
usbguard
    (below generates rules based on all currently attached devices)
    usbguard generate-policy > /etc/usbguard/rules.conf
    usbguard.service

ESSENTIAL:
firefox             web browser
vlc                 media player
libreoffice-still   office suite (stable)
steam               games
retroarch           retro games
    retroarch-assets-xmb
    retroarch-assets-ozone


VIRTUALIZATION:
qemu libvirt iptables-nft dnsmasq bridge-utils openbsd-netcat virt-manager edk2-ovmf
    libvirtd.service

PRINTING:
cups                        printing
    #cups.service
    cups.socket
cups-pdf                    print to pdf
    Change pdf save location /etc/cups/cups-pdf.conf
system-config-printer       auto-driver install


OPTIONAL:
obs-studio          capture and streaming
spotifyd            music app (open source third party)
discord             chat app (proprietary)

